node.text: "But if we learned anything from sports, is that no matter how far down we may be, we are never too far down to come back."
The Houston-based rapper brings his workwear touch to Nike SB, adding bandana patterns, rope-style fat laces, and more to the fat-tongued gem.

node.text: The Parley x adidas UltraBOOST '21 is unlike anything we've seen. While this partnership typically involves application of its recycled plastics into the upper, this upcoming project transforms the upper into one of the more impressive takes on the UB franchise in recent memory. Tap the link in our bio to get a closer look.

node.text: With adidas selling Reebok, this Shaqnosis could be the last of the signature shoe crossovers. Tap the link in our bio to see a detailed look at this Dame x Shaq mash-up; these will drop on 9/1 in EU.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Sneaker News on August 30, 2021 tagging @endclothing. May be an image of footwear.

node.text: Tan/neutral tones on the Air Jordan 4 have a track record of being absolute hits. Will this women's "Shimmer" live up to that standard? Hit the link in our bio to see the store list; these are scheduled to release on September 3rd.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sneaker News on August 30, 2021. May be an image of footwear and text that says 'NIKE LIKE TRUE TO YOUR CITY. There is Dunk for everyone. And now there is one for Tokyo.'.

node.text: @fujiwarahiroshi drops a clever teaser for his upcoming fragment x Nike Dunk High "Tokyo" by altering the classic "Be True To Your School" ad. What other cities should Hiroshi usher in? Hit the link in our bio for more details.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sneaker News on August 30, 2021. May be an image of footwear.

node.text: New Balance hones in on school colors for this 550 "Team Pack". All three drop on September 1st; hit the link in our bio to see all three in detail.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Sneaker News on August 30, 2021 tagging @zsneakerheadz. May be an image of footwear.

node.text: This Air Jordan 13 Low for Greater China covers the silhouette in Barely Green and Black, while a signature dimpled upper has its dots connected to form a constellation detail. Hit the link in our bio for a closer look; these are expected in November.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Sneaker News on August 30, 2021 tagging @repgod888. May be an image of footwear and outdoors.

node.text: One of several colorways of the Travis Scott x Nike Air Max 1 gets revealed up close. While the giant reverse swoosh has worked for the AJ1, how's it look for the AM1? Tap the link in our bio to see a closer look.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sneaker News on August 29, 2021. May be an image of footwear.

node.text: Anyone getting Mars Yard vibes with this upcoming Nike Dunk High Rebel release? This transformed women's shoe is set to arrive soon in the ever-popular pairing of tan and red tones; hit the link in our bio to see more.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sneaker News on August 29, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and footwear.

node.text: Zion Williamson's Jordan Zion 1 signature is now offered in a variety of TB (Team Bank) colorways. They've got five covered, but what other team uniform colors should exist? Hit the link in our bio to see all five.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sneaker News on August 29, 2021. May be an image of footwear.

node.text: Nike's Sisterhood series continues with this attractive take on the Air Max 97; from a cream sail to a bright crimson, a subtle gradient provides a distinct look befitting the Sisterhood theme. For a closer look, tap the link in our bio.
